{
  "stem": "1400.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I saw the chimney, day and night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At night, flames were going out of the chimney, and the stench of the burned human body was always around us, constantly.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] And so, after that, as I say, I didn't work by then on the kitchen and of the period during the last month or three weeks while I was in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was in the detail, emptying the barrels which were in each barracks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They-- at night, we couldn't go out of the barrack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they had barrels for necessities.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so we had to put this on the wagon and push it out on the field.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And after this crematorium was blown up, I witnessed-- ah-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the Nazis made the prisoners dig big ditches.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was like a foundation of a house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Long ditches-- and they carried in a layer of wood, a layer of bodies, a layer of wood, a layer of bodies.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they dose it with gasoline.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were burning bodies in an open pit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were walking by this at one time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] And so as I say, after this, I exchanged myself for a piece of bread and got out of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But this is my physical-- I-- things, what I mainly remember, the most horrifying, and-- I'm not talking about the daily beating and atrocity.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the kapos, I don't know if-- later we learned that the different triangles meant different people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had the gypsies with this color, and the Jews had  the yellow triangle, and the gays had the pink triangle.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the criminals of-- the German criminals, because there were no prisons, they were the kapos-- the black triangle.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were mainly-- they were the kapos.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
